high_descs: Turn left then face the end of the tub
Pick up the candle on the tub beside the soap
Turn right then head to the cabinet below the sink
Open the cabinet and put in the candle then close the cabinet
Turn right then move to the right side counter of the sink
Pick up the candle on the sink counter
Turn left then head to cabinet
Open the cabinet and put in the candle then close the cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put the two candles in the cabinet

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the front of the bath tub.
Pick up the candle on the front of the bath tub.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the left side of the sink.
Place the candle in the drawer on the left of the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the candle on the sink.
Pick up the candle on the sink.
step to the left to face the left side of the sink.
Place the candle in the drawer on the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place two candles in the drawer on the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the counter, then turn right and walk over to the wall.
Pick up the candle off of the tub.
Turn right and walk to the toilet. then walk to the counter on your right.
Open the second lower drawer from the left below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
Walk up to the right side of the counter in front of you.
Pick up the candle off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the tub, then turn right and walk towards the door, turn right again to face the counter.
Open the second lower drawer from the left below the counter and put the candle inside, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move two candles into a drawer.
